{"tid":931138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【玩大佢】烏克蘭決定不延續與俄羅斯友好條約　又擴大領海範圍","createTime":"2018-12-06T23:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T04:24:14.000Z","uid":37661,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f351b872d0141f9253d81817bba7d3d780babfd8","tid":931138,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T23:20:22.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭決定不延續與俄羅斯友好條約　又擴大領海範圍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vR8uZPd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvR8uZPd.png&h=46cd81f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭總統波羅申科一身迷彩打扮，視察一個空軍基地。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n2018-12-07 HKT 05:52<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭與俄羅斯緊張關係繼續升級，烏克蘭國會通過，不會延續與俄羅斯的友好條約，又單方面擴大領海範圍。<br />\n<br />\n烏俄友好條約原定明年4月續期，但國會採納總統波羅申科的動議，不會延續。<br />\n<br />\n國會又通過法案，把領海範圍擴大一倍至24海里。當局說，此舉可讓海岸防衛隊和海軍更有效巡邏，防止軍事威脅和走私活動。法案同時容許烏克蘭邊境守衛，不用警告就可向潛在攻擊者開火。<br />\n<br />\n波羅申科到一個空軍基地視察，他宣布派遣空中突擊隊前往俄羅斯邊境，加防邊防力量。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯至今仍扣押烏克蘭海軍3艘艦艇和24名船員。出席歐洲安全與合作組織會議的烏克蘭外長要求俄羅斯釋放船員，讓他們安全回國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432130-20181207.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432130-20181207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=H4T%2BPylf5ae9qr21ynUjI7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=220902b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432130-20181207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=caa5b33d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432130-20181207.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"33bf05919c9078e8bbe2947bd116ed46d9da80cb","tid":931138,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T23:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbef970f807f1ef53c92ad632e2c9a1dceb118ab","tid":931138,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T23:50:53.000Z","msg":"唉怕撚左你成日想打交<br />\n<br />\n香港人幫你地